content.rendered:
Directed by Mrighdeep Lamba.

Written by Vipul Vig. Mrighdeep Lamba.

Cast Pulkit Samrat(Hunny). Varun Sharma(Choocha). Ali Fazal(Zafar). Manjot Singh(Lali). Richa Chadha(Bholi Punjaban). Priya Anand(Priya). Pankaj Tripathi(Pandit (as Pankaj Tripathy)). Vishakha Singh(Neetu Singh). Pallavi Batra(Receptionist at Hotel). Purnendu Bhattacharya(Brijmohan). Monsoon Boruah(Tibetian Daughter). Aman Chaudhry(Lawyer). Vijay Kumar Dogra(Bank Executive). Mahesh Gahlot(Priya’s Father). Mayank Gola(Student In College). Rajiv Gupta(Minister Babulal Bhatia). Jamuna Kapoor(Tibetian Lady). Majinder Singh Kareer(Billa). Sachin Kathuria(Injured Man at Bholi Den). Gurpreet Kaur(Lal’s Mother). Gulnaaz Khan(Meri Mehbooba Dancer). Ishtiyak Khan(Tidda). Sumit Khanna(Varun’s Friend & Financer). Neelu Kohli(Choocha’s Mother). Ravi Kothari(Second Reporter). Olanokiotan Gbolabo Lucas(Bobby). Manil Mishra(Reporter at Tibetian Colony). Manil Mayank Mishra(Reporter). Chang Mum(Chinese Guy). Nalneesh(Mangu). Nalneesh Neel(Mangu). Micheal Obodike(Eddie). Lucas Ogunro(Bobby). Musa Muhammed Olayinka(Ravi). Ashok Pathak(Smackiya). Sadanand Patil(Changu). Sanjana Sanghi(Katty). Bharat Sharma(Hotel Staff at Suite). Khushbu Sharma(Female Reporter at Speech). Raj Sharma(Music Composer). Harsh Shashwat(Digital Partner). Gurneet Singh(Broker). Rubneil Singh(Sardar Kid). Natasa Stankovic(Lead Dancer O Meri Mehbooba). Alkesh Tiwari(Choocha’s Father). Chitranjan Tripathi(Eunuch). Chayan Trivedi(Doctor). V S Prince Ratan(News Reporter). Shrikant Verma(Babulal’s PA)

Language Hindi.

Producers Farhan Akhtar. Kyle Ambrose. Vikesh Bhutani. Kaushik Guha. Umesh Pawar. Stuti Ramachandra. Ritesh Sidhwani. Chanpreet Singh.

Production Excel Entertainment.
